Admin - FPO Applications


GET
/api/admin/applications/
List FPO applications


Paginated list of all FPO applications. Filter by status, district, tier, or search by name/application_id.

Parameters
Cancel
Name	Description
district
string
(query)
Filter by district code (e.g. TSR, KLM)

district
search
string
(query)
Search by FPO name or application_id

search
status
string
(query)
Filter by FPO status (draft/submitted/under_review/approved/rejected/info_required/suspended)

status
tier
string
(query)
Filter by tier (A/B/C/D)

tier
