POST
/api/admin/applications/{fpo_id}/request-info/
Request additional information from FPO


Transitions APPROVED → INFO_REQUIRED. FPO user receives email with the notes and can re-submit once they have addressed the request.

Note: Since approval is automated, admin raises info requests on an already-APPROVED FPO.

Parameters
Cancel
Name	Description
fpo_id *
integer
(path)
3
Request body

application/json
Examples: 
Request info
Edit Value
Schema
{
  "notes": "Please upload a clearer copy of the bank statement."
}
Execute
Responses
Code	Description	Links
200	
No response body

No links



