POST
/api/admin/applications/{fpo_id}/assign-tier/
Manually assign tier to an FPO


Admin override — manually assign a tier (A/B/C/D) to an FPO for a specific financial year.

Creates a new FPOTierHistory record and syncs FPO.tier immediately.

Use this when the auto-scored tier needs correction.

Request body:

{ "tier": "A", "financial_year": "2026-27", "notes": "Manually verified — exceptional performance" }
Parameters
Cancel
Name	Description
fpo_id *
integer
(path)
fpo_id
Request body

application/json
Edit Value
Schema
{
  "tier": "A",
  "financial_year": "0632-49",
  "notes": "string"
}
Execute
Responses
Code	Description	Links
200	
No response body

No links



GET
/api/admin/audit-logs/
List audit log events


Paginated audit trail of all system events. Supports filtering by action type, FPO, user, and date range.

Available action types: create, update, delete, soft_delete, restore, login, logout, failed_login, password_change, password_reset, export, import, document_upload, document_delete, fpo_profile_change, fpo_submit, fpo_status_change, tier_recalculation, fpo_user_invite, fpo_user_activate, fpo_user_deactivate

Parameters
Cancel
Name	Description
action
string
(query)
Filter by action type

action
fpo_id
integer
(query)
Filter by FPO ID — shows all events on that FPO

3
from_date
string
(query)
Start date (YYYY-MM-DD)

from_date
to_date
string
(query)
End date (YYYY-MM-DD)

to_date
user_id
integer
(query)
Filter by user who performed the action

user_id
Execute
Clear
